STEEL MANUFACTURERS (STL)
AUTO PARTS AND EQUIPMENT INCLUDING TIRES (AUP)
</IN>
<LP>
   Kloeckner-Werke AG, said it is buying a British-owned
plastics company and is close to selling its Mannstaedt steel
unit to British Steel PLC.
   The West German steel, plastics and machinery group said
it has agreed to buy Eurotec Systemteile G.m.b.H., a maker of
