                                Jun 4     Jun 1     Year
                                                                                                       

   U.S. ......................  339.2     334.9   +  4.4
   Britain ...................  707.6     704.6   -  1.9
   Canada ....................  397.0     395.6   -  8.2
   Japan ..................... 1367.5    1369.2   - 17.4
   France ....................  584.9     584.9   +  3.2
   Germany ...................  296.6     296.6   +  4.0
   Hong Kong ................. 2347.6    2361.7   + 12.0
   Switzerland ...............  226.8     226.8   +  2.7
   Australia .................  310.9     307.6   -  6.1
   World index ...............  526.8     528.0   -  7.2
